data.title: #1 IN WOMEN'S BASKETBALL
data.meta_description: Perform with purpose – Elevate your game in sneakers built by and for female hoopers.
data.text:
"These shoes are super special to me because I based the colorway around my college, the University of South Florida. If it wasn't for that school and basketball program, I wouldn't be here still doing what I love, so it was only right I show love." -Courtney Williams #10

"I love that Moolah Kicks is a brand that exclusively supports and elevates women’s basketball. Having shoes that are made specifically for women’s feet makes a huge difference. They are so comfortable; I love playing in them." -Caroline Ducharme #33

"Being from NYC and seeing how Women’s basketball evolved over the years has been great. But being from NYC and having the first women’s shoe to be instilled and used in their own very courts is amazing. I’m from NYC so you already know I’m rocking with Moolah." -Kateri Poole #55

"Moolah Kicks are definitely a top of the line basketball sneaker. My first time putting a pair on they were super comfortable and so light. I haven’t looked back since. On top of the sneaker being a great fit. I love what Moolah stands for and for that reason I continue to represent the brand." -Imani Tate #2

"What I like about Moolah Kicks is their drive to not only provide female athletes with a sneaker specifically for us but also with a platform and a business that is both genuine and consistently working hard to positively change how the world views women in sport." -Taylor Soule #13

"I love Moolah because it represents the Female Baller. Not to mention, the cool name, the color ways, and Natalie being a fun energy!!" -Niki Avery

"Moolah Kicks has impacted the comfort level of my feet while I’m hooping on the court. They’ve been the perfect addition to my bag and have impacted my play." -Aijha Blackwell #33

"Being able to be a part of an organization that is pushing the growth of women’s athletics and equality has been such a joy. Moolah Kicks is changing the game for every female baller." -Eva Hodgson #10

"I love wearing and working with Moolah. Not only does it make my feet feel the best, the brand encourages me to be my best as it pushes for women’s representation and empowerment." -Marnelle Garraud #14

"I loved being a part of a brand made for women. It feels great to see an amazing shoe grow over time. The designs never disappoint and always have a little something for everyone. I was honored to be able to share this wonderful organization with anyone willing to listen." -Uju Ezeudu #24

"As an athlete I have benefited from wearing Moolah Kicks. Not only are these shoes built for a women’s foot, they also create major comfort for the soles of your feet. Moolah Kicks have so much foot support and keeps me light on my feet. Thank you, Moolah Kicks, for having me a part of your team, this organization will change the dynamic of women basketball." -Tishara Morehouse

"Working with Moolah Kicks was a great experience, they truly embrace women’s sports and promote the empowerment of women all over the country! The shoes themselves are so comfy to play in!" -Faith Masonius #13
